Need to make a change to your upcoming rental? Now you can edit your requests and bookings without having to cancel the original booking. You’re able to change all parts of your booking, including the start and end times, adding an extra driver, and purchasing more kilometers.

In this latest release car owners will see a new and improved calendar to manage their car’s availability. More calendar features like adding a repeating unavailability every week are coming soon!

We’ve also made it easier for new renters to add a profile picture when requesting a car, because car owners generally like to see who is asking to borrow their car.
This latest release includes the ability to sign-up and sign-in using your Apple ID.

- Car owners can now set a maximum period that their car can be rented out for
